snippet.title: Echoes of the Plum Grove | Release Date Announcement | Freedom Games
snippet.description:
Your next cozy farming gaming obsession, Echoes of the Plum Grove, is coming to Steam on April 29, 2024! 

Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1536090/Echoes_of_the_Plum_Grove/?utm_source=FG&utm_medium=RDA&utm_campaign=YT 

A new life awaits in Honeywood! Build a thriving community that will last generations in this cozy farm simulator. Farm, socialize, make friends, cook, craft, forage and uncover the secrets of the island! If someone doesn’t want to be friends? There are always other means.
